reasingly intelligent, interconnected yard networks where automation and AI drive continuous improvement. You have the opportunity now to position your operations at the forefront of sustainable supply chain management. Adopting advanced YMS technology isn't just about meeting today's environmental standards—it's about building resilient, efficient logistics operations ready for tomorrow's challenges.",[19674],{"type":149,"attrs":19675},{"color":1233},{"id":18,"url":18,"linktype":19,"fieldtype":20,"cached_url":18},[2788],{"id":139,"alt":139,"name":18,"focus":139,"title":139,"source":139,"filename":18,"copyright":139,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":19679},{},"How a Yard Management System Can Reduce Idle Time and Emissions",{"id":19682,"alt":18,"name":18,"focus":18,"title":18,"source":18,"filename":19683,"copyright":18,"fieldtype":1105,"meta_data":19684,"is_external_url":49},110546816656797,"/storyblok/f/337048/1592x1110/054fc499cf/x.webp",{},[],"Learn how a modern yard management system cuts idle time and lowers emissions—helping logistics operations improve sustainability without sacrificing speed or efficiency.",{"value":2818,"plugin":2819},"sustainability-in-motion-how-a-yard-management-system-can-reduce-idle-time-and-emissions","all-resources/sustainability-in-motion-how-a-yard-management-system-can-reduce-idle-time-and-emissions",-1080,[4660,4661,4662,2826],"0cebc329-88db-4b2c-aeb4-f8dd0e0fe9b1","2025-11-18T15:02:41.165Z",[],{"name":19696,"created_at":19697,"published_at":19698,"updated_at":19699,"id":19700,"uuid":19701,"content":19702,"slug":20608,"full_slug":20609,"sort_by_date":139,"position":20610,"tag_list":20611,"is_startpage":49,"parent_id":2828,"meta_data":139,"group_id":20612,"first_published_at":20613,"release_id":139,"lang":1161,"path":139,"alternates":20614,"default_full_slug":139,"translated_slugs":139},"Best Dock Scheduling Software for Efficient Warehouse Operations","2025-09-19T08:33:50.604Z","2026-03-27T17:47:30.656Z","2026-03-27T17:47:30.678Z",924